<div class="banner">
  <div class="text-center ms-auto me-5 w-50">
    <h1>We Help You Take Care Of <br>Your Plants</h1>
    <p>A beaufitul home doesn't have to be a struggle to maintain. <br>With Plant Helper, there is never the need to worry about your plants health. <br>Our website is made to cater to every environemnt. <br>Fill in your homes details to see your plants strive better than ever before.</p>
    <div class="container CTA-container">
      <% if current_user == nil || current_user.onboarded == false %>
        <%= link_to "/my_plants", class: "CTA" do %>
          <button type="button" class="call-to-action-landing-page standard-button btn btn-primary">
            Help your plants!
          </button>
        <% end %>
      <% else %>
        <%= link_to "/dashboard", class: "CTA" do %>
          <button type="button" class="call-to-action-landing-page standard-button btn btn-primary">
            Check your tasks!
          </button>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="info-cards-under-hero">
  <div class="below-hero-cards">
    <div class="image-in-hero-card">
     <%= image_tag "dove.png", class: "below-hero-card-image-styling" %>
    </div>
    <h2 class="card-heading">MINDLESS CARE</h2>
    <p class="card-paragraph">Taking care of your greenery has never been easier. Get reminders straight to your email when you sign up!</p>
  </div>

  <div class="below-hero-cards">
    <div class="image-in-hero-card">
      <%= image_tag "planting.png", class: "below-hero-card-image-styling" %>
    </div>
    <h2 class="card-heading">CONSTANT MONITORING</h2>
    <p class="card-paragraph">Follow your plants life on Your Plants and watch them grow along the way</p>
  </div>

  <div class="below-hero-cards">
    <div class="image-in-hero-card">
      <%= image_tag "plant-tree.png", class: "below-hero-card-image-styling" %>
    </div>
    <h2 class="card-heading">HEALTHY PLANTS</h2>
    <p class="card-paragraph">Our algorythm calculates the perfect watering cycle for your garden.</p>
  </div>
</div>
